      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im on sertraline for my anxiety but the side effects are like making me feel super nauseous and weird all the time. i saw online that st johns wort is basically the same thing but just natural and doesnt have all those chemicals. can i just stop the sertraline and start taking st johns wort instead? would that work okay?",
